subject: Update of Junit.org
msgSnippet: Hi, I am wondering if anyone knows how to contact the web master of junit.org.  I noticed today that in the IDEs section it is missing the support of JUnit
messageBody:
Hi,

I am wondering if anyone knows how to contact the web master of
junit.org. I noticed today that in the IDEs section it is missing the
support of JUnit within JBuilder itself, although this feature has been
there since 2001 and has been updated for usability.

Thanks
Shane
